_comment: target: must be of format [team/]name, do not prefix the org, or suffix with version
version: must be specified
application: Application of model
framework: Framework of model
model_format: Format of model
precision: Precision of model
short_description: Short description of model
overview_filename: Overview filename of model. Defaults to null
bias_filename: Bias_filename of model. Defaults to null
explainability_filename: Explainability filename of model. Defaults to null
privacy_filename: Privacy filename of model. Defaults to null
safety_security_filename: Safety security filename of model. Defaults to null
display_name: Display name of model. Defaults to null
labels: Label of model. Defaults to null - the format is a list of strings
label_sets: Label set of model. Defaults to null - the format is a list of strings
logo: Logo of model. Defaults to null - the format is url
public_dataset_name: Public dataset name of model. Defaults to null
public_dataset_link: Public dataset link of model. Defaults to null
public_dataset_license: Public dataset license of model. Defaults to null
built_by: Time of model built by. Defaults to null
publisher: Publisher of model. Defaults to null
source: Source location of model. Defaults to the current directory
gpu_model: GPU model of model. Defaults to null
memory_footprint: Memory footprint of model. Defaults to null
num_epochs: Epoch number of model. Defaults to null
batch_size: Batch size of model. Defaults to null
accuracy_reached: Accuracy of model. Defaults to null
description: Description of model. Defaults to null
link: Link of model. Defaults to null
link_type: Link type of model. Defaults to null
dry_run: Is this a dry run. Defaults to false
credential_files: List of Credential files of model with full path. Defaults to null
metric_files: List of Metric files of model with full path. Defaults to null
